
---

### 2. **`index.html`**
**Purpose:** Entry point for the app.  
**Contents:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Endless</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main id="canvas-container"></main>
    <script src="sketch.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
